name: CryptoMushrooms #004 - Psilocybe Cubensis
description:
The most well know and used psychedelic/hallucinogenic mushroom, due to its wide distribution and ease of cultivation, it grows in a variety of climates and habitats around the world. It is also know as “Magic Mushroom”, “Golden Tops”, “Philosopher's Stones”, “Shrooms” and many other names. It’s principal active compounds are psilocybin and psilocin, that triggers psychedelic experiences after ingestion, and may lead to visual and mental hallucinations, space and time distortion, increased creative visualization, and so on. It also can cause nausea, anxiety, frightening, introspective experience, nervousness, paranoia, panic, hallucinations, and psychosis.
